    • Island

      public Island​(DrawingSurface surface, processing.core.PImage cImage, int circeX, int circeY, int houseX, int houseY)
      Creates a new island in the provided surface, given the location of Circe and her house.
      Parameters:
      surface - the PApplet on which this island may be drawn
      circeX - the x coordinate of Circe
      circeY - the y coordinate of Circe
      houseX - the x coordinate of Circe's house
      houseY - the y coordinate of Circe's house
      houseSize - the size (length of the side) of Circe's house
